Groovy Scripting Handling Exceptions and Collections:

def terms=["SOAPUI", "Training", "online","IT"]
log.info terms[0]
log.info terms[3]
for(def i=0;i<4;i++)
{
	log.info terms[i]
}
//Exceptions
try
{
def x=4/0	
}
catch(Exception e)
{
	log.info "script not able to handle"
}
//Array List
ArrayList ar = new ArrayList()
ar.add("a")
log.info ar.get(0)
ar.add("b")
log.info ar.get(1)
//HashTable (Key, value)
